column1: bcG5Zf7X,BWR - Changelog 21/08/23,SSilver,Diff,Monday 21st of August 2023 05:46:05 PM CDT,Sniper Rifles
~ Reserve ammo is set to 16, no more fake bullet
~ Added HYPE jump sound effect when using HYPE
Provide better feedback to enemies on scout's mobility
~ Added BONK effect over marked targets heads
+ Reverted debuff duration time to 7s max (was 5s max)
+ Minimum distance for debuff duration decreased to 175 HU
Item's debuff seemed too hard to capitalize on, so it buffed to allow for a better window.
Weapon appeared underwhelming at it's main niche, so increasing the potential health while keeping its damage reined in should help the weapon promote sustainability.
+ Reverted: Collect the organs of people you hit
~ Changed: 400 points of healing instead gives one Organ
~ Changed On teammate hit: heals them for 50% HP per Organ, up to their max overheal
+ Added Alt-Fire: use 3 organs to guarantee a critical hit on your next hit!

Reintroducing the old organ collecting and segmenting the potential healing in more distinct chunks, done in order to limit the potential healing from more passive play while also reintroducing the risk/reward of the prior version to provide your team with support.
- Added: Minicrits whenever it would normally crit
Attempting to make the weapon better stand by providing a stronger opening shot without crits while reining in the potential damage from farmed crits."
